Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差點害死康拉德大尉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好 輕一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中打開艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且想要和敵方駕駛員接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛…在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐基利亞是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你應該戰鬥的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己應該保護的對象都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛不是敵人 她保護了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止吧 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為強制解除聯結 很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對門外漢認真可不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算駕駛valiancer 他也是平民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒道理把軍人的自尊強加給他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 我們不用游泳回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有你 我們這兩次可能都要掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說太多話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我們的救世主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意 我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:53.39,an8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說叫你不要說話了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦現在開始為了進行損傷各處的修理以及補給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往習志野基地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦保持第一警戒配備 嚴密戒備
