Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:17.71,zm,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,300)\pos(584,530)}兩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:17.71,zm,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,300)\pos(630,530)}用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:17.71,zm,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,300)\pos(675,530)}迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:17.71,zm,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,300)\pos(721,530.667)}擊
