Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通路連接展開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,estifit引導 航海開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通路連接接受 連鎖開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量罩打開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,emphatier等級上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯結需要兩人意志統一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 必須要互相信任 互相接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而妨礙它的因素有多個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最主要的是感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是報告過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們關係還不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,valiancer隊 進入戰鬥空域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 就這樣打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦接近民營船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道打算依附在上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是野蠻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以只攻擊FLAMBERGE嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 離得那麼近 民營船也會受到傷害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個紋章是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 難怪敵人會盯上它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了 竟然一個人突破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉君 聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個船 似乎是迪奧老家的船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧的家人也可能在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 大概是在上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韋恩伯格家在聯合也是非常有名的名門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果抓做人質 就可以進行各種交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是敵人的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算是迪奧 那也是一個人無法解決的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能不會再見到家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我非常瞭解你焦急的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人 應該保護的人就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我保護他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 再一次進行聯結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,emphatier等級上升
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達可以聯結領域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯結完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 剛才那是什麼動作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民營船脫離了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民營船正在脫離 已到炮擊範圍外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 青葉君 聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們繼續護送民營船 從千歲進港
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是千歲基地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
