Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 連迪奧·韋恩伯格的臉都忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲奧娜 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台valiancer果然是迪奧呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該做的 不是在這種地方偷懶吧
